      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn52.12:1.1",
          "pli": "“Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhomi—ekopi hutvā bahudhā homi … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattemī”ti. ",
          "en": "“… And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that I wield the many kinds of psychic power: multiplying myself and becoming one again … controlling the body as far as the Brahmā realm.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn52.12:1.2",
          "pli": "Dutiyaṃ. ",
